    "props": {
      "resourceNotes": "<p>This provides an additional bonus die on all Etiquette tests to gain dossiers and two bonus dice when using the Leadership skill outside of combat.</p><p>An additional asset is available for hire each sector turn per resource class of the network.</p><p>This resource lowers the neighborhood class by an additional level (for example, a rank B back alley network provides +4 available assets for hire each sector turn, for a total of 7, and counts as a class C resource when calculating sector class).</p><p>Building a back alley network is affordable and reduces costs to build by 80% (2,000 Zuzus per condition box).</p><p>Building a back alley network does not consume a resource slot in the sector.</p>",
      "buildingTags": "Service",
